{"tid":1555081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔敢跳閘者入］黨鐵全日通優惠上線啦","createTime":"2019-09-09T08:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:20:43.000Z","uid":48124,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c94c7754def5b6439d3936b6315b5195c5a725a","tid":1555081,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"見到最近有唔少巴打分享跳閘既經歷同心得<br />\n但都同時見到有人話唔敢跳/ 手無力/ 驚人捉/ 唔想成焦點/攞住重野....<br />\n到底點至可以光明正大咁入閘上車又唔洗送全費比黨鐵賺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長者卡故然係一個方法, 但比人捉到一樣有口實話你無資格用優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂「堅持 堅持幾多錢一茶匙丫？ 你都咁大個仔啦 有乜為？窮到日日搭地鐵偷雞用特惠」<br />\n但我堅持我堅持到有一日   俾地鐵罰左五百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而有一個方法, 可以比連「日日搭地鐵偷雞用特惠」都唔敢既人....就係買正價單程飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由出發站起計買最近站既單程飛, 光明正大入閘上車, 出閘時至跳閘/ 低調推閘/ 闊閘機低調跟人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多數查票員都係入閘後收費區至check, 大家入閘比人check既咪show張單程飛比佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到回程/ 去其他地方時...照袋好同一張單程飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出入閘都係低調推閘/ 闊閘機低調跟人行<br />\n比人check到會點啊?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乘客若入閘後逗留超過150分鐘，無論是在原站或在另一個站出閘，需繳付相等於當時最高之成人單程車費作為附加費，以現時車費計算，即為$61.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罰則係咪輕過$500好多呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重要既係心理壓力問題, 要明白唔係人人都夠膽直接跳閘<br />\n但當你係一個「持有有效車票」既人, 只係唔小心搭過龍/ 係站裹面shopping耐左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你既成本只係需要補返一餐lunch既價錢<br />\n<br />\n每人既膽/覺得自己可以承擔既風險都唔同,  當大家慢慢過左個心理關口, 就可以慢慢上升level:<br />\nLevel 1 「持有真 - 有效車票」: 照比原價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但會跳閘/推閘去cover其他手足<br />\nLevel 2 「持有有效車票」: 正價(最近一站既)單程飛, 全日任跳任推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLevel 3 「持有特惠車票」: 長者卡/ 特惠單程飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同時跳閘/推閘去cover其他手足<br />\nLevel 4 「扮持有車票」: 用無八達通既銀包扮拍卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />低調推閘/ 闊閘機低調跟人尾<br />\nLevel 5 「什麼是車票」: 高調跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都要唱返首456wing<br />\n一齊「大大步走上前, 大大步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走, 屬於你自己嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"f9da6803b470a3976851bf912ab555048587af9e","tid":1555081,"uid":98852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:35:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6b31350d87de623612242a861737f18885f32bf0","tid":1555081,"uid":259044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2ff2ef9b9f6e90c594b4ab5083be115940603d46","tid":1555081,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"Wow!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04814aea5543198099f3659e89ce9f5451e4c87","tid":1555081,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a70536a2ca25bb7bd264a41a7bddf4206bca64","tid":1555081,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26b4c72d486fa9f0ac77e73262473744640f98d8","tid":1555081,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"［黨鐵的事］ 唔夠力跳玻璃欄嘅巴絲入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544834</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9650f629f2a942c46d796277113197e50943c9f","tid":1555081,"uid":309617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"日日level5緊 啱啱又跳完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789e5eb8a23debad37474e5dc6ecbb8b8cce7074","tid":1555081,"uid":136793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"Level 4真係好容易，絲都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好怕！特別闊閘機！<br />\n跟人行同推閘上哂癮"}]}